577
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,100
Not exactly, but kind of.

578
00:34:17,420 --> 00:34:18,700
And there's a competition too?

579
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,140
It's the first competition.

580
00:34:21,180 --> 00:34:22,700
