584
00:34:34,220 --> 00:34:35,100
Then go for it.

585
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:40,180
You support me?

586
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:45,900
Since you want to, just go.

587
00:34:46,420 --> 00:34:47,700
Don't worry about your mom.

588
00:34:48,340 --> 00:34:49,220
I'll get it covered.

589
00:34:50,420 --> 00:34:51,380
Go confidently.

590
00:34:55,900 --> 00:34:56,740
I thought

