618
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:18,700
to give you and your mom

619
00:36:18,700 --> 00:36:20,580
the life you two wanted.

620
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:24,180
But today, when I heard you
talking to Xiaolan,

