626
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:48,060
So,

627
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:51,340
if you want to go, just go.

628
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:54,700
The vow I made earlier

629
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:56,220
still counts now.

630
00:36:57,140 --> 00:36:58,540
I can support you,

631
00:36:58,540 --> 00:36:59,380
don't worry.

632
00:37:01,580 --> 00:37:02,420
Thank you, Dad.

633
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:05,860
This is the only role I can play.

634
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:08,700
Thank you, Dad.

